/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪on9架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自殺條款是指在保險合同生效後的一定時期內被保險人自殺死亡屬於除外責任，保險人不給付保險金，僅退還所繳納的保險費；而保險台同生效滿一定期限後被保險人因自殺死亡，保險人要承擔保險責任，按照約定的保險金額給付保險金。<br />\n<br />\n兩年內自殺先唔賠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你覺得好唔合理?<br />\n而且我完全唔係做保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5569822eb7f1c17f89951b7757b180df65475fab","tid":92290,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:44:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每個月要供幾多？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"aadd0359bdbd59c5469a1ad1cf01340c141eddf3","tid":92290,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有抑鬱症比唔比你買？</blockquote>"}]}